reviewText: BriBri  -  You'll watch "real video" of dead bodies but this is gross to you.  True, Faces of Death is despicable and I have the decency not to watch this **** but so is watching any dvds or videos that depict real life murders, accidents, etc... You people need serious psychological help for watching crap like this.
i mean what do u expect, ofcourse its gonna be brutle but just  not enough shock, mostly boring n just dead bodies,,this movie was so short not even an hour long :((( don't waste your time!!

I really don't mind gross out movies, or "real video" of dead bodies etc. But this nightmare of a film is totally exploitative. It preys on the unfortunate victims of violence,accidents, drive by's, murders, etc. The movie must have been made by total immoral animals who would turn out their sisters into prostitution. I mean the producers of this pure s--- must be grade A 100 PROOF PSYCOPATHS!!! Stay the hell away from this, to financially support this garbage would be a crime...
